<br>
Use your summoned line of spells, rarely resisted and<br>
they are mana efficient. Also give your pets the Sword of Runes that you can summon it procs a summon spell.<br>
My pets proced it quite often.<br>
<br>
Park pet near the castle on the island and pull to there.<br>
If you get an over pull just run to the top of the tower<br>
and click on the magic portal to zone in to Fungus Grove<br>
to clear the agro. Don't stay too long in FG though. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Like type elelmentals are social and will help each other but differing types wont. A fire will not help a water, etc.<br>
<br>
Pull the fire elementals with cancel magic to get rid of their fire shield and then they are whimps.<br>
<br>
There are vendors in the zone to sell to. The elementals<br>
drop crappy spiny weapons but they sell for a about 5 gold. The elementals drop a TON of spell research components so its a good place to stock up.<br>
<br>
I flew through 29-35 here. Wish I knew about it before that probably good for 24-35 or so. At 36 there will be too many greens for me to stay.<br>
<br>
Very easy hunting here highly recommended.<br>
<br>
